# Real-tester data — contains tester names + typed reflections (PII).
# Calibration values from these runs are integrated into DEFAULT_CALIBRATION
# in src/sdk/attention-protocol.js as anonymized scalars; the raw artifacts
# stay local. Do not commit these archives.
#
# Round-2 narrowing (2026-04-28): the original `proof/results/` directory
# rule was too broad — it excluded the canonical demo fixtures
# (stephen-0573-anchored.json, humanness-sample.json,
# verify-sample-{6,7}layer.json) which carry NO PII (anonymized scalars
# only) but ARE the regression-test inputs for canonical-fixtures.test.js.
# CI was failing because the fixtures aren't checked in.
#
# Approach: ignore proof/results/* by default (timestamped bot runs, live-
# roundtrip outputs, signed-jwts archives — none of which are required at
# build/CI time), then explicitly un-ignore the 4 canonical fixtures plus
# the openbadge sample. Add new fixtures by name as they're created.
proof/real_tests_apr26/
proof/results/*
!proof/results/stephen-0573-anchored.json
!proof/results/stephen-0573-signed.json
!proof/results/stephen-openbadge-sample.json
!proof/results/humanness-sample.json
!proof/results/verify-sample-6layer.json
!proof/results/verify-sample-7layer.json
proof/Results-*.zip
public/proof/Results*.zip
